info: Rating, 5 stars,  · May 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: Great host and very accommodating. I put up my mother for several days as our own place was getting fixed. He was understanding and genuinely concerned. I would recommend his place without a doubt.
I really enjoyed my 3 days here. The host was friendly and like family. Highly recommended if you come to Bangladesh.
It's a very family-like and comfortable atmosphere. They also serve delicious local food. Recommended!
It's a really cozy and nice place to stay! The owner is really kind and friendly. Recommended if you come to Bangladesh.
